original_title: Underwater Hotel - Life On Artificial Reefs
overview: A sunken vessel carries with it a treasure of stories and mysteries that can only be guessed at by today's divers and researchers. This captivating program allows you to tag along with a dive team on a voyage to explore various South Pacific wrecks. You'll view plenty of astounding wreck footage, as well as a host of fascinating species that inhabit the reefs of these majestic seas. The documentary features music by Indigenous Australia.
title: Underwater Hotel - Life On Artificial Reefs
